Q) How does Docker Compose differ from Kubernetes?
    - Compose is simpler, for local/dev use.
    - Kubernetes is production-grade, scalable, and has a full orchestration engine.

Q) Can you run multiple Compose projects on the same host?
    Yes, by setting a custom project name:

        docker-compose -p myproject up


